, New York pp. 1209\u20131218 (2012). doi:<span class=\"ExternalRef\">\u00a0<a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" href=\"https://doi.org/10.1145/2207676.2208572\"><span class=\"RefSource\">10.1145/2207676.2208572</span></a></span>\n        <span class=\"Occurrences\"></span></div></li><li class=\"Citation\"><div class=\"CitationNumber\">11.</div><div class=\"CitationContent\" id=\"CR11\">Goodwin, K.: Perfecting your personas (2008). <span class=\"ExternalRef\"><a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" href=\"http://www.cooper.com/journal/2008/5/perfecting_your_personas\"><span class=\"RefSource\">http://www.cooper.com/journal/2008/5/perfecting_your_personas</span></a></span>\n        <span class=\"Occurrences\"></span></div></li><li class=\"Citation\"><div class=\"CitationNumber\">12.</div><div class=\"CitationContent\" id=\"CR12\">Goodwin, K.: Designing for the Digital Age: How to Create Human Centered Products and Services. Wiley, NewYork (2009)<span class=\"Occurrences\"><span class=\"Occurrence OccurrenceGS\"><a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" class=\"google-scholar-link gtm-reference\" data-reference-type=\"Google Scholar\" href=\"http://scholar.google.com/scholar_lookup?title=Designing%20for%20the%20Digital%20Age%3A%20How%20to%20Create%20Human%20Centered%20Products%20and%20Services&amp;author=K.%20Goodwin&amp;publication_year=2009\"><span><span>Google Scholar</span></span></a></span></span></div></li><li class=\"Citation\"><div class=\"CitationNumber\">13.</div><div class=\"CitationContent\" id=\"CR13\">LeRouge, C., Ma, J., Sneha, S., Tolle, K.: User profiles and personas in the design and development of consumer health technologies. Int. J. Medical Inf. <strong class=\"EmphasisTypeBold \">82</strong>, 251\u2013268 (2013). doi:<span class=\"ExternalRef\">\u00a0<a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" href=\"https://doi.org/10.1016/j.ijmedinf.2011.03.006\"><span class=\"RefSource\">10.1016/j.ijmedinf.2011.03.006</span></a></span>\n        <span class=\"Occurrences\